HELP:
To run a command in the server, use `@ZevBot#6253 command` or `!command`.
For example, `@ZevBot#6253 faq`.
To view  a list of all valid commands, use !help all
COMMANDS:
__**All Commands**__


								__ToMemeText__
Can accept a string of any length as a parameter.
Will return a copy of that string in alternating case.
Example: eXaMpLe


									__FAQ__
If used without any parameters, it will display a list
of valid questions you can pass in as parameters.
All questions are case insensitive.
Example: !faq Release date


If you have an idea of a Command, just send @minim#3100 a DM with the idea.
